phrases=["Man Cannot remake himself without suffering., for he is both the marble and the sculptor.","The greatest glory in living lies not in never falling, but in rising every time we fall.","Stop talking and Start doing.","If you set your goals ridiculously high and it's a failure, you will fail above everyone else's success.","A successfull man is one who can lay a firm foundation with the bricks others have thrown at him.", "Don't be afraid to give up on the good to go for the great.", "Success is walking from failure to failure without losing enthusiasm.","The only place where success comes before work is in the dictionary.","Don't judge each day by the harvest you reap but for the seed that you plant.","It is in our darkest moment when we must focus to see the light.","Go where there is no path and leave a trail.","In the end, it's not the years in your life that count. It's the life in your years.", "The only impossible journey is the one that you never begin.", "You only live once, but if you do it right, once is enough.", "Courage is doing what you don't dare to do.", "The woods would be silent if only the birds with good voices sang.", "Without courage the other virtues lack sense.", "Learn from yesterday, live for today and have faith for tomorrow.", "Without pressure there wouldn't be any diamonds.", "You do not find a happy life, you make it.", "Impossible is for the unwilling.", "Believe that you can and you will be half way there.", "It's never too late to be what you could be.", "Hell is where you meet who you could have been.", "You must do things you think you can't do.", "Your mission in life is not only to survive, but to thrive.", "To be the best you must be able to handle the worst.", "It's always darkest before dawn.", "The best revenge is a massive success.", "You were not born to be a second-hander.", "Everything is practice.", "If you are going through hell, keep going.", "We can do anything we want to if we stick to it long enough.", "There is no saint without a past, no sinner without a future.", "Pain is temporary. Quitting lasts forever.", "No great thing is created suddenly.", "No wind favors he who has no destined port.", "Trees that are slow to grow bear the best fruit.", "Yesterday you said tomorrow.", "None preaches better than the ant, and she says nothing.", "Ask for what you want and be prepared to get it.", "I’m a slow walker, but I never walk back.", "Don’t wish it was easier. Wish you were better.", "The mind is everything. What you think you become.", "Shoot for the moon, even if you fail, you’ll land among the stars.", "You miss 100% of the shots you don’t take.", "The higher we soar the smaller we appear to those who cannot fly.", "Dreams don’t work unless you do.", "Skill is only developed by hours and hours of work.", "The most difficult thing is the decision to act, the rest is merely tenacity.", "Continuous effort – not strength or intelligence – is the key to unlocking our potential."]
